bpa

Interface BpaCostsMaker

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BpaCostsMakerAbstract, BpaCostsMakerImplCSV, BpaCostsMakerImplSQL

    public interface BpaCostsMaker
    A class that implements BpaCostsMaker needs to: - Create a BpaCosts file. - Populate the BpaCosts file with the Bpa costs of a period.
